text.tspan: 1. Place the bottom of the bottle into the water.
Untwist handle and pull up to draw water into
2. When filled with water, push the handle back
down and twist to lock into place. The elastic
silicone band inside the bottle pulls the plunger
down, applying pressure onto the water.
3. Drop the bottle back into the HeroPak and
twist onto their filter. Water will then flow into
the filter from the water pressure.
